=Check whether this candidate video is substantially the same idea as any past video.

=== PAST VIDEOS (most recent first) ===
{{ JSON.stringify($json.dedup_context || []) }}

=== CANDIDATE ===
Title: {{ $json.idea_title }}
Summary: {{ $json.idea_one_line_summary }}
Hook: {{ $json.idea_hook }}

Rules:
- 'Substantially the same' = same core insight, even if framing differs.
- Different example, same insight = duplicate.
- Same topic, different insight = NOT duplicate.
- Be moderately strict, not paranoid.

Return ONLY valid JSON:
{ "duplicate": true|false, "similar_to": "title or null", "reason": "one sentence" }

